{"tid":723324,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV奪《東方華爾街》播映權","createTime":"2018-06-30T09:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T09:48:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe97800b04b8e18948d28d01294c47cbdcd51ca1","tid":723324,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180630/20435609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F20435609&d=B05o93hk5VrN2Ye05TDvFZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ce2cb9ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F20435609&h=f3ad9ba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180630/20435609</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月30日 <br />\n<br />\nViuTV奪《東方華爾街》播映權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180630/large/1530279470_1eff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180630%2Flarge%2F1530279470_1eff.jpg&h=afee703d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■嚴嘉念（中）前晚宣佈《東》劇會於ViuTV免費頻道播出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180630/large/30ec2p11a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180630%2Flarge%2F30ec2p11a.jpg&h=dbba3d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華仔與《東》劇主要演員在尖沙嘴慶功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由劉德華監製、黃國強導演，吳鎮宇、張孝全、余男、陳家樂、江奇霖、蔡潔和潘燦良等主演，譚耀文和張可頤特別演出，以香港金融為題材，一共五集的原創迷你劇《東方華爾街》，經已在網絡上播放完畢，口碑不錯。如果錯過網絡收看的戲迷，仍然有機會再睇，事關ViuTV取得播映權，將於稍後在免費頻道播出。<br />\n<br />\n劉德華前晚聯同導演、吳鎮宇、張孝全和張可頣等一眾主要演員在尖沙嘴出席《東》劇慶功宴，FOX高級副總裁嚴嘉念前晚在宴會上除了宣佈《東》劇會於ViuTV免費頻道播出之外，並透劉正計劃開拍第二季，劉德華都表示希望有機會可以再和大家一起參與演出。ViuTV方面則回應指：「播放詳情將於稍後公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：魯吉  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【冥王星有生物？】NASA發布爭議照片　科學家、天文學生各有解釋│噼啪&times;Professor PowPow<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n羅霖無力談戀愛"}]}